<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Sinatra Playlister Lab - Artists</title>
    <style>
    body {background-color: black;}
    h1 {color: silver; font-family: verdana;}
    p {color: silver; font-family: verdana;}
    a {text-decoration: none; color: powderblue;}
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>This is a page for Playlister Artists</h1>
    <p>If I had put any seed data here there would be an array of artists following this message.</p>
    <p>(What do you know. There's seed data. Ish.)</p>
    <% @artists.each do |artist| %>
        <p><a href="/artists/<%= artist.slug %>"><%= artist.name %></a></p>
    <% end %>
  </body>
</html>